Robert Tomanovich owns Robert's Discount Tree Service in Livonia, Michigan . 
  He first hung a noose from a tree and a Confederate flag on a fence at his home . 
  A second noose was hung on a tree outside his business after neighbours complained . 
  Tomanovic has denied his actions are racist and said he simply liked the colors of the flag . 
  Wife said the flag was a tribute to a friend who hung himself . 
 